  "detailed_description": "Bad Guy: Neighborhood is a unique open world free roam style game. Complete objectives, mini games, and fight bosses to earn money and unlock unique items and abilities in the store. Encounter special enemies and find hidden secrets as you explore a violent and unpredictable neighborhood. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.poster.avif?t=1767055537\" width=510 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.webm?t=1767055537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.mp4?t=1767055537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15+ unique weapons and abilities<br></li><li>Unique Arrest/\"Police\" system<br></li><li>Special date-able characters<br></li><li>5 boss fights to beat<br></li><li>Objective and task progression system<br></li><li>Time rated mini-games<br></li><li>Borderline psychopathic game-play options<br></li><li>Unknown secrets that unlock super secret things (very secret)<br></li><li>Continuous open-world, do whatever you want<br></li><li>Chaotic NPCs constantly fighting/killing each other<br></li><li>Customizable NPC amount (more/less chaos)<br><br><br></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Bad Guy: Neighborhood is a unique open world free roam style game. Complete objectives, mini games, and fight bosses to earn money and unlock unique items and abilities in the store. Encounter special enemies and find hidden secrets as you explore a violent and unpredictable neighborhood. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.poster.avif?t=1767055537\" width=510 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.webm?t=1767055537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772620/extras/c8833bbe7f3c39e138ccacafa7784feb.mp4?t=1767055537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15+ unique weapons and abilities<br></li><li>Unique Arrest/\"Police\" system<br></li><li>Special date-able characters<br></li><li>5 boss fights to beat<br></li><li>Objective and task progression system<br></li><li>Time rated mini-games<br></li><li>Borderline psychopathic game-play options<br></li><li>Unknown secrets that unlock super secret things (very secret)<br></li><li>Continuous open-world, do whatever you want<br></li><li>Chaotic NPCs constantly fighting/killing each other<br></li><li>Customizable NPC amount (more/less chaos)<br><br><br></li></ul>",
